NK016(ma)012:0: na rag dong sprugs phyag rgya gcig pa'i khrid yig zab lam snang byed ces bya ba bzhugs so //
NK016(ma)012:2: rnam 'gyur chos kun lhag pa bden pa gnyis //
NK016(ma)012:3: dbyer med chos sku chen por byang chub pa //
NK016(ma)012:4: bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i zhabs btud nas //
NK016(ma)012:5: dong sprugs khrid yig zab lam snang byed brtsam //
NK016(ma)012:6: 'dir bskyed rdzogs gsum gyi sgor zhugs pa'i rnal 'byor
NK016(ma)012:7: pa rnams kyi spyi khrus na rag dong sprugs kyi
NK016(ma)012:8: lam zab mo nyams su len pa'i rim pa la
NK016(ma)012:13: 'gal rkyen gyi spros pa bcad pa dang /
NK016(ma)012:14: mthun rkyen gyi yan lag mngon du bya ba gnyis /
NK016(ma)012:16: 'khor ba'i bya ba ngan pa la zhen pa'i gnyen por dal 'byor rnyed dka' bsam pa dang /
NK016(ma)012:17: tshe 'dir spyod yul la chags pa dang le lo
NK016(ma)012:18: snyoms las kyi gnyen por 'chi ba mi rtag par
NK016(ma)012:19: bsam pa dang / srid pa'i bde ba la chags
NK016(ma)012:20: shing zhen pa'i gnyen por 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal bzod
NK016(ma)012:21: glags med par bsam pa'i skyo shas kyis yid bskul
NK016(ma)012:22: te thar 'dod kyi blo bcos ma ma yin par
NK016(ma)012:30: dang po skyabs 'gro la kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis kyi /
NK016(ma)012:32: gnas khang dag pa'i zhing du mos te /
NK016(ma)012:33: mdun gyi nam mkhar seng ges btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la /
NK016(ma)012:34: bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'i rnam pa can skyabs gnas kun 'dus kyi ngo bor bsam la /
NK016(ma)012:35: rang gzhan sems can thams cad 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal
NK016(ma)012:36: gyis 'jigs nas skyabs zhu na ci mdzad bla ma
NK016(ma)012:39: bla ma bde gshegs 'dus pa'i sku //
NK016(ma)012:40: dkon mchog gsum gyi rang bzhin la //
NK016(ma)012:41: bdag dang 'gro drug sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)012:42: byang chub bar du skyabs su mchi //
NK016(ma)012:43: zhes rnam rtog gzhan gyi sel ma zhugs par mang du bzla /
NK016(ma)012:45: bla ma 'od du zhu ba rang la bstim ste
NK016(ma)012:46: 'khor gsum mi dmigs pa'i ngang nas bla ma'i rdo
NK016(ma)012:47: rje gsum dang rang gi lus ngag yid gsum dbyer
NK016(ma)012:48: med la rtse gcig mnyam par 'jog /
NK016(ma)012:49: gnyis pa sems bskyed la'ang kun rdzob dang don dam gnyis las /
NK016(ma)012:51: rang gzhan sems can thams cad gdod ma nas rang bzhin rnam dag gi sangs rgyas yin kyang /
NK016(ma)012:52: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis 'khor bar sdug
NK016(ma)012:53: bsngal ba rnams la tshugs thabs med pa'i snying rje
NK016(ma)012:54: chen pos / de rnams sdug bsngal las bsgral te
NK016(ma)012:55: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi go 'phang la
NK016(ma)012:56: chen pos / 'god par bya / de'i ched du zab mo'i lam bsgom par bya'o snyam pas /
NK016(ma)012:57: bdag dang mtha' yas sems can rnams //
NK016(ma)012:58: ye nas sangs rgyas yin mod kyang //
NK016(ma)012:59: rtog pa'i dbang gis 'khor ba las //
NK016(ma)012:60: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK016(ma)012:62: gnyis pa don dam sems bskyed ni /
NK016(ma)012:63: de ltar sems bskyed pa'i sems de skye 'gag gnas
NK016(ma)012:64: dmigs 'gro 'ong dang bral ba'i ngang la rtse gcig
NK016(ma)012:67: e ma'o ngo mtshar rmad kyi chos //
NK016(ma)012:68: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kun gyi gsang //
NK016(ma)012:69: skye ba med las thams cad skyes //
NK016(ma)012:70: skyes pa nyid na skye ba med //
NK016(ma)012:71: de bzhin du skye ba'i gnas su /
NK016(ma)012:76: tshig dang mthun par don bsam zhing slar yang mnyam par 'jog go //
NK016(ma)012:77: gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i sngon 'gro la /
NK016(ma)012:78: mchod pa la brten nas bsod nams kyi tshogs stobs su bya ba dang /
NK016(ma)012:79: dbang gi ye shes gsal btab pa la brten nas ye shes kyi tshogs stobs su bya ba gnyis /
NK016(ma)012:81: rang nyid gnyug ma'i lhar gsal ba'i thugs ka'i 'od
NK016(ma)012:82: kyis reg pas snod bcud thams cad mi dmigs par
NK016(ma)012:83: sbyangs / stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang dag pa'i zhing khams yangs shing rgya che bar gyur /
NK016(ma)012:84: rang gi mdun gyi nam mkhar seng ge chen po
NK016(ma)012:85: brgyad kyis btegs pa'i rin po che'i khri pad nyi
NK016(ma)012:87: rang gi rtsa ba'i bla ma de nyid dpal rdo
NK016(ma)012:88: rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam pa can du
NK016(ma)012:89: gsal ba'i thugs ka nas 'od zer 'phros /
NK016(ma)012:90: dus gsum gyi bla ma dkon mchog gsum yi dam
NK016(ma)012:91: zhi khro mkha' 'gro chos skyong rnams spyan drangs nas
NK016(ma)012:93: de la phyi mchod kun bzang /
NK016(ma)012:97: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs te /
NK016(ma)012:98: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK016(ma)012:99: zhes mtheb srin gyis phul bas bdud rtsi ro brgya
NK016(ma)012:100: ldan pa'i rgyun bla ma yab yum gyi zhal du
NK016(ma)012:101: gsol bar bsam / gsang mchod ni /
NK016(ma)012:102: rang gi thugs ka nas rig ma mtshan nyid dang
NK016(ma)012:103: ldan pa spros te bla ma'i yum la thim nas
NK016(ma)012:104: snyoms 'jug mdzad pa'i bde ba'i nyams bskyangs te mnyam
NK016(ma)012:105: par bzhag / de kho na nyid kyi mchod pa ni /
NK016(ma)012:106: rang nyid kyang bla ma'i yum la thim nas snyoms
NK016(ma)012:107: par zhugs te bde ba'i nyams skyes pa de ka'i
NK016(ma)012:108: ngang la khrug chil gyis gyur par blta'o //
NK016(ma)012:109: gnyis pa ye shes kyi tshogs stobs su bya ba ni /
NK016(ma)012:110: bla ma'i thugs ka nas rang nyid mar me gcig
NK016(ma)012:111: las gnyis mched kyi tshul du ngo bo rdo rje
NK016(ma)012:112: sems dpa' la rnam pa tha mal pa'i tshul du
NK016(ma)012:114: badz+ra sa m+aa dzahs mdun gyi nam mkhar bla ma
NK016(ma)012:115: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum rang gi spyi bor
NK016(ma)012:116: spyan drangs la / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK016(ma)012:117: sa ma ya hoh a nu r+aa ga y+aa mi /
NK016(ma)012:121: s+pha ra na phata ces sbyor mtshams nas 'od zer spros /
NK016(ma)012:122: sems can thams cad kyi ma dag pa'i rgyud sbyangs /
NK016(ma)012:123: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs dam bskul te /
NK016(ma)012:124: sam ha ra na h'u zhes pas thabs kyi cha thams cad yab dang /
NK016(ma)012:125: shes rab kyi cha thams cad yum la bsdus nas /
NK016(ma)012:126: bla ma yab yum sangs rgyas kun 'dus kyi ngo
NK016(ma)012:127: bor mos la ba spu ldang zhing mchi ma 'khrug
NK016(ma)012:128: pa'i mos gus kyi gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK016(ma)012:129: bla ma chos kyi sku la gsol ba bdebs //
NK016(ma)012:130: bla ma longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la gsol bla
NK016(ma)012:131: ma sprul pa'i sku la rgyal ba dgongs brgyud bla
NK016(ma)012:132: ma la rig 'dzin brda brgyud bla ma la gang
NK016(ma)012:133: zag snyan brgyud bla ma la dbyer med rdo rje
NK016(ma)012:134: sems dpa' la 'gal rkyen spros pa chod par byin
NK016(ma)012:135: gyis rlobs // mthun rkyen mngon du 'gyur bar byin
NK016(ma)012:136: sems lnga rgyud la skye bar dbang bzhi nyams su
NK016(ma)012:137: longs par ting 'dzin rnam gsum rtogs pa skye bar
NK016(ma)012:138: cir snang lha sku'i 'khor lor 'char bar grags pa
NK016(ma)012:139: brjod bral sngags sgrar 'char bar 'gyu ba rang rig
NK016(ma)012:140: bde ba chen por 'char bar nyams chag rtog sgrib
NK016(ma)012:141: dbyings su dag pa srid zhi mnyam pa nyid du
NK016(ma)012:142: rtogs par lhag pa bden pa dbyer med kyi gnas
NK016(ma)012:143: lugs rtogs par sku lnga ye shes lnga ldan kun
NK016(ma)012:144: bzang rdo rje sems dpa'i go 'phang bdag gzhan sems
NK016(ma)012:145: can thams cad kyis thob par byin gyis rlobs shig
NK016(ma)012:146: gyis rlobs // / ces gsol ba ci mang btab
NK016(ma)012:147: pas bla ma rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi
NK016(ma)012:148: sbyor mtshams nas byang sems bdud rtsi'i rgyun babs pa
NK016(ma)012:149: lus ngag yid gsum la thim pas sgo gsum gyi
NK016(ma)012:150: gyis rlobs // / dri ma dag / bum gsang
NK016(ma)012:151: sher dbang gsum thob pas rdo rje gsum gyi dngos
NK016(ma)012:153: bla ma yab yum bde ba'i ngo bor zhu ba
NK016(ma)012:154: rang gi snying gar babs pas sgo gsum phra ba'i
NK016(ma)012:155: sgrib pa dag / gnyis su med pa ye shes
NK016(ma)012:156: rdo rje'i rang bzhin tshig dbang rin po che rang
NK016(ma)012:158: ye shes rdo rje'i dngos grub la dbang 'byor bar
NK016(ma)012:159: bsam la dar cig klod de mnyam par bzhag go
NK016(ma)012:160: // gnyis pa dngos gzhi la bzhi /
NK016(ma)012:161: rdo rje sems dpa' bum pa'i dbang gi nyams len
NK016(ma)012:162: bsgom bzlas la brten nas nyams chag dang rtog sgrib
NK016(ma)012:164: mkha' 'gro ma gtor ma'i dbang gi nyams len gtan
NK016(ma)012:165: pa med pa'i mchod spyin chen po la brten nas
NK016(ma)012:166: rang bzhin dbyings kyi mkha' 'gro dang gnyis su med
NK016(ma)012:168: rig ba'i rtsal dbang gi nyams len lhag pa'i ye shes ngos bzung ba'i man ngag /
NK016(ma)012:169: dam pa rigs brgya phyag rgya'i dbang gi nyams len
NK016(ma)012:170: snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad dag pa'i
NK016(ma)012:171: snang ba rab 'byams su bstan pa'i man ngag go
NK016(ma)012:173: shu nya t+aa'i sngags kyis 'di ltar snang ba'i chos
NK016(ma)012:174: thams cad mi dmigs shing sbros pa dang bral ba'i
NK016(ma)012:175: ngang la dar cig mnyam par 'jog pa ni de
NK016(ma)012:176: bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin chos thams cad kyi
NK016(ma)012:177: gnas lugs de bzhin nyid yin pa la /
NK016(ma)012:178: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i sgyu ma lta bu'i sems
NK016(ma)012:179: can rnams la 'dzin med sgyu ma lta bu'i snying
NK016(ma)012:180: rje mkha' khyab tu sgom pa ni kun snang gi
NK016(ma)012:181: ting nge 'dzin / stong nyid snying rje zung du
NK016(ma)012:182: 'jug pa'i rang rig a yig dkar po bde gsal
NK016(ma)012:183: stong pa nyid kyi rang bzhin du sgom pa ni
NK016(ma)012:185: thog mar de gsum la nyams lnga'i rim pa dang sbyar nas sgom /
NK016(ma)012:186: de nas rang gi sems nyid a yig las h'u
NK016(ma)012:187: gi sgra gdangs nam mkha' gang bar spros pa las
NK016(ma)012:188: rdo rje'i sa gzhi rwa gur ye shes kyi me
NK016(ma)012:189: dpung mtha' med du 'phro bas phyogs kun gtam te
NK016(ma)012:190: cis kyang mi shigs pa'i srung ba'i 'khor lor gyur
NK016(ma)012:191: pa'i nang du ye shes rin po che 'bar ba'i
NK016(ma)012:192: gzhal yas khang mtshan nyid thams cad yongs su rdzogs
NK016(ma)012:193: pa'i dbus su / seng ge brgyad kyis btegs pa'i
NK016(ma)012:194: rin po che'i khri pad nyi zla ba'i gdan la
NK016(ma)012:195: rang gi sems nyid a dkar babs /
NK016(ma)012:196: de yongs su gyur pa las h'u yig sngon po gsal zhing 'bar ba /
NK016(ma)012:198: sangs rgyas kyi mdzad pa bsgrubs /
NK016(ma)012:199: slar 'dus yongs su gyur pa las rdo rje sngon po /
NK016(ma)012:200: de las 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten khams kyi
NK016(ma)012:201: thabs kyi cha thams cad bsdus te thim pa yongs
NK016(ma)012:203: rang nyid bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing ga zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK016(ma)012:204: zhi zhing rab tu 'dzum pa'i mdangs gsal ba'i zhal
NK016(ma)012:205: gyi 'gyur ba ting nge 'dzin gyi rnam par rol
NK016(ma)012:206: pa'i nyams can mtshan dang dpe byad kyis 'bar ba
NK016(ma)012:207: / phyag g.yas rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin cing /
NK016(ma)012:208: g.yon dril bu dkur brten pas yum la 'khyud pa /
NK016(ma)012:209: dbu skra ral pa'i thor tshugs can /
NK016(ma)012:210: zhabs gnyis rdzogs pa'i skyil mo krung gis brtan par bzhugs pa /
NK016(ma)012:211: yab kyi thugs ka nas m+aum chad /
NK016(ma)012:212: 'od zer 'phro 'dus yongs su gyur pa las dril bu /
NK016(ma)012:213: de las 'od zer 'phros pas 'jig rten khams kyi
NK016(ma)012:214: shes rab kyi cha thams cad bsdus te thim pa
NK016(ma)012:216: yab kyi g.yon phyogs nye ba'i pang du yum rdo
NK016(ma)012:217: rje dbyings phyug ma sngon mo g.yas dril bu 'dzin
NK016(ma)012:219: g.yon rdo rje rang gi thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK016(ma)012:220: brtul zhugs kyi skyil mo krung gis 'khril ba /
NK016(ma)012:221: gnyis ka'ang zhi ba'i rgyan chas bcu gsum gyis spras shing /
NK016(ma)012:222: zhi ba'i nyams dgu rgyas pa /
NK016(ma)012:223: 'od zer kha dog drug gi snang ba re re'ang
NK016(ma)012:224: bye ba phrag drug drug tu 'phro ba'i klong na
NK016(ma)012:225: bzhugs pa / yab yum gnyis kyi thugs kar rang
NK016(ma)012:226: 'dra'i ye shes sems dpa' rgyan dang phyag mtshan spangs
NK016(ma)012:227: pa re re'i thugs kar zla ba la h'u dang
NK016(ma)012:228: m+aum yig sngon po rtag tu 'char bzhin pa /
NK016(ma)012:229: de las byung ba'i 'od zer gyis phyogs bcu dus
NK016(ma)012:230: bzhi'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa thams cad rdo
NK016(ma)012:231: rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rnam par spyan drangs
NK016(ma)012:232: / chu la chu bzhag pa ltar rang lus la dbyer med du khrug gis bsre /
NK016(ma)012:233: slar yang thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas
NK016(ma)012:234: dbang gi lha mi bskyod pa gtso bor gyur pa'i
NK016(ma)012:235: rigs lnga yab yum gyi rnam par spyan drangs /
NK016(ma)012:236: rigs lnga yab yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad /
NK016(ma)012:237: rjes chags kyi mes zhu ba'i ye shes lnga'i chu
NK016(ma)012:238: rgyun mgo bo'i gnas lngar babs te dbang bskur bas
NK016(ma)012:241: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas su gnas gyur /
NK016(ma)012:242: chu lhag ma spyi bor brtan pa las mi bskyod
NK016(ma)012:243: pa bdag por gyur pa'i rigs lnga sprul sku'i cha
NK016(ma)012:244: byad can gyis dbu brgyan par bsam /
NK016(ma)012:245: slar yang spyi bor zla ba la dkar po /
NK016(ma)012:246: mgrin par pad+ma la +aam dmar po /
NK016(ma)012:247: snying gar nyi ma la h+au sngon po /
NK016(ma)012:248: de gsum las 'phros pa'i 'od zer gyis rdo rje
NK016(ma)012:249: gsum gyi lha tshogs nam mkha' gang bar spyan drangs
NK016(ma)012:250: te yi ge so so la thim pas de bzhin
NK016(ma)012:251: gshegs pa thams cad kyi rdo rje gsum dang gnyis
NK016(ma)012:253: yi ge so so yongs su gyur pa las /
NK016(ma)012:254: spyi bor sku rdo rje dkar po 'khor lo //
NK016(ma)012:255: mgrin par gsung rdo rje dmar po pad+ma /
NK016(ma)012:256: snying gar thugs rdo rje sngon po rdo rje 'dzin pa rnams kyis rgyas btab par bsam /
NK016(ma)012:257: slar yang snying ga'i h'u gi 'od zer gyis phyogs
NK016(ma)012:258: bcu dus bzhi'i rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa mkha'
NK016(ma)012:259: khyab tu sad par byas te /
NK016(ma)012:260: rang la dbyer med du khrug gis 'dres par bsam
NK016(ma)012:261: pa yang nas yang du bzla ba ni ye shes
NK016(ma)012:262: sems dpa' bskyar bsnan gyi sbyor ba'o //
NK016(ma)012:263: de nas sku'i gsal snang la sems rtse gcig tu bzhag /
NK016(ma)012:264: mi gsal na 'phro bcad la wal gyis gsal 'debs /
NK016(ma)012:265: gsal na de ka'i rgyud la yud tsam sems bzhag ste 'phro bcad /
NK016(ma)012:266: yang bsgom pa sogs yang yang gsal btab la sems bzung /
NK016(ma)012:267: lha sku'i rnam pa spyi dang bye brag so sor
NK016(ma)012:268: sbyangs bas gsal snang thon mtshams nas lha sku dwangs
NK016(ma)012:269: gsal rnyog pa med pa me long nang gi gzugs
NK016(ma)012:270: brnyan shar ba lta bu la rtse gcig tu mnyam
NK016(ma)012:271: par 'jog / res zhu bdes drangs nas de ga'i
NK016(ma)012:272: rang ngo la ce re bltas te bde stong gi
NK016(ma)012:273: lha skur 'char ba la slob cing /
NK016(ma)012:274: yang rang sems lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med kyi
NK016(ma)012:275: lha'i skur rnam par dag pa'i nges shes bskyed la
NK016(ma)012:277: nyams lnga ci rigs ma skyes kyi bar du rtse gcig tu bsgom par bya'o //
NK016(ma)012:278: gal te sgom pas skyo na thugs ka'i h'u yig
NK016(ma)012:279: gi mthar yi ge brgya ba'i sngags phreng kha dog
NK016(ma)012:280: dkar po g.yas bskor du 'khor ba la sems bzung
NK016(ma)012:281: ste bzlas pas / sngags phreng las byung ba'i 'od
NK016(ma)012:282: zer gyis rgyal ba sras dang bcas pa'i thugs dam
NK016(ma)012:283: ste bzlas pas / bskul / bdag dang mkha' khyab
NK016(ma)012:284: kyi de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi zhal nas
NK016(ma)012:285: sngags kyi sgra dang thugs rje'i 'od zer 'phros pas
NK016(ma)012:286: khams gsum thams cad snang bar byas /
NK016(ma)012:287: las dang nyon mongs pa thams cad sbyangs /
NK016(ma)012:288: na raka sogs ngan song gi gnas rnams dong nas sprugs te /
NK016(ma)012:289: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas kyi zhing du bsgral /
NK016(ma)012:290: 'od zer rnams slar 'dus te sngags phreng la thim /
NK016(ma)012:291: snang grags 'gyu gsum lha sngags 'od gsal gyi 'khor lor sbyangs te /
NK016(ma)012:292: yig brgya nyer gcig las mi nyung ba bazla'o //
NK016(ma)012:294: snod bcud kyi snang ba thams cad 'od du zhu ba spyi bo'i rigs bdag la thim /
NK016(ma)012:295: rigs bdag kyang rang la thim /
NK016(ma)012:296: rang ye shes sems dpa' la /
NK016(ma)012:297: de ting 'dzin sems dpa' h'u la /
NK016(ma)012:303: de yang mi dmigs par thim nas rnam par rtog
NK016(ma)012:304: med lhun grub nam mkha' lta bu'i ngang la klod
NK016(ma)012:306: thun las ldang ba na rdo rje sems dpa' snang
NK016(ma)012:307: stong sgyu ma lta bu'i skur langs te snang grags
NK016(ma)012:308: 'gyu gsum la lha sngags 'od gsal gyi 'khor los
NK016(ma)012:309: rgyas btab ste / spyod lam thams cad lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi rol par spyad par bya'o //
NK016(ma)012:311: rnam par mi rtog pa ka dag de kho na nyid kyi ngang las /
NK016(ma)012:312: de ltar ma rtogs pa'i mkha' khyab kyi sems can la sgyu ma lta bu'i snying rje bskyed /
NK016(ma)012:313: de'i ngang las snod kyi 'jig rten ka p+aa la
NK016(ma)012:314: yangs shing rgya che ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pa
NK016(ma)012:315: / de'i nang du rgya tshad med pa'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor skya 'khyil la ba /
NK016(ma)012:316: de'i steng du bcud rang gzhan sems can thams cad
NK016(ma)012:317: kyi gnas lus longs spyod dge ba'i rtsa ba dang
NK016(ma)012:318: bcas pa thams cad rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK016(ma)012:319: dam tshig gi rdzas sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga'i ngo
NK016(ma)012:320: bor phung gis song ba la /
NK016(ma)012:321: sangs rgyas thams cad kyi ye shes dang ro mnyam
NK016(ma)012:322: pa'i bdud rtsi'i dwangs ma chu bo'i rgyun bzhin du
NK016(ma)012:323: babs pa ro gcig tu 'dres pas ye shes kyi
NK016(ma)012:324: bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por mer gyis song bar
NK016(ma)012:325: bsam / de nas mkha' khyab kyi 'khor lor bzhugs pa'i mchod yul thams cad dang /
NK016(ma)012:326: sems can thams cad kyang dag pa'i snang ba 'ba' zhig tu sad pas /
NK016(ma)012:327: 'khor 'das thams cad mchod yul du dag pa'i sku
NK016(ma)012:328: gsung thugs kyi gsang ba rang bzhin dbyings kyi mkha'
NK016(ma)012:329: 'gro mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo dang rang
NK016(ma)012:330: gi lus ngag yid gsum ro gcig pa bde ba
NK016(ma)012:331: chen por 'bar ba la sems mnyam par bzhag ste
NK016(ma)012:333: rtsa brgyud kyi bla ma dam pa yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams /
NK016(ma)012:336: rigs drug gi sems can lha'i 'khor lor dag pa
NK016(ma)012:337: dang bcas pa thams cad kyi zhal du kha kha
NK016(ma)012:340: lus ngag yid gsum gyi nyams byung rgyal du bskyang bar bya ste /
NK016(ma)012:341: srid zhi ro mnyam pa'i sbyor bas bya'o //
NK016(ma)012:343: stan bde ba la lus gnad rkang pa rdo rje skyil krung /
NK016(ma)012:348: so mchul bar yod par byas /
NK016(ma)012:349: mig rdzi ma 'thab rdeb dang mig 'bras mi 'gul bar ce re blta /
NK016(ma)012:350: ngag gnad rlung rang babs su bzhag /
NK016(ma)012:351: sems gnad rang gi snying gar zla ba la kun
NK016(ma)012:352: tu bzang po mthing ga rdor skyil mnyam gzhag gi
NK016(ma)012:353: phyag rgya can / sku dwangs shing sgrib pa med
NK016(ma)012:354: pa 'od kyi rang bzhin can cig gsal btab pa
NK016(ma)012:355: la ched 'dzin med par yid gtad de /
NK016(ma)012:358: dus gsum gyi rtog pa gang yang yid la mi byed par rang babs su mnyam par 'jog cing /
NK016(ma)012:359: de ga'i rang ngo la ce re blta /
NK016(ma)012:360: de ltar bltas pas gang du'ang ngos bzung med cing /
NK016(ma)012:361: blo'i yul las 'das pa'i gsal rig rjen pa spros pa dang bral ba zhig 'char bas /
NK016(ma)012:362: de ka ye shes lnga'i rang bzhin kun tu bzang po'i thugs te /
NK016(ma)012:363: de ka'i ngang rtsol bral bsal bzhag med par bskyang bar bya ste /
NK016(ma)012:365: sngar rjes mi bcad 'das pa'i 'du shes dor //
NK016(ma)012:366: phyis sngun mi bsu yid kyi 'brel thag bcad //
NK016(ma)012:367: bar du 'dzin med nam mkha'i ngang la bzhag /
NK016(ma)012:370: rig pa sems kyi ngo bo nyid /
NK016(ma)012:371: spros med rnam dag ye shes yin //
NK016(ma)012:372: kun gzhi ye nas ma bcos pa //
NK016(ma)012:373: bde chen rang shar klong du zhog /
NK016(ma)012:375: gzhan yang de'i tshe sems kyi gshis snang rig ngos
NK016(ma)012:376: bzung bral ba la rang gdangs bde chen du ma
NK016(ma)012:378: bsgom bya sgom byed las 'das pa'i yul med rang gsal du cham gdal ba ste /
NK016(ma)012:380: snang stong dbyer med chos sku la //
NK016(ma)012:381: rig stong bde ba chen por shar //
NK016(ma)012:382: zung 'jug spros dang bral ba de //
NK016(ma)012:383: kun tu bzang po'i ngo bo'o //
NK016(ma)012:385: de ka la gnas na legs /
NK016(ma)012:386: gal te rnam rtog 'phro na gang shar de ka'i rang ngo la ce re bltas pas /
NK016(ma)012:387: skyes zin skye 'gyur skye bzhin pa'i rtog pa thams cad wal khyug gis song nas /
NK016(ma)012:388: rang shar rang grol gyi ye shes gsal ba mi rtog par rjen lhag gis 'char te /
NK016(ma)012:389: de ka'i ngang la ched 'dzin med par shigs se rang lugs su bskyang bar bya'o //
NK016(ma)012:390: de ltar mnyam rjes thams cad la dran pa bdag
NK016(ma)012:391: por gyur pa'i sgo nas skad cig kyang yengs pa
NK016(ma)012:392: med par byar med blo 'das gnyug ma'i ye shes
NK016(ma)012:393: kyi ngang la gnas shes pa'i thag chod skye zhing
NK016(ma)012:394: / dge sbyor rkyen thub skyong bde mor 'gro ba la tshegs med do //
NK016(ma)012:396: 'di ltar snang ba sna tshogs su snang ba phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang /
NK016(ma)012:397: nang bcud kyi sems can thams cad kyi rang bzhin
NK016(ma)012:398: nam gshis tshul ye gdod ma nas rnam par dag
NK016(ma)012:399: pa yin kyang / de ltar ma rtogs te las
NK016(ma)012:400: kyi bgo skal la spyod pa 'di dag la bcos
NK016(ma)012:401: min gyi snying rje chen po bskyed /
NK016(ma)012:402: don dam par 'khor 'das rgyud gcig tu shes pas
NK016(ma)012:403: snod bcud dag snang gi 'khor lo sangs rgyas thams
NK016(ma)012:404: cad dang ro gcig tu blta /
NK016(ma)012:405: de thams cad rang sems lhag pa bden gnyis dbyer med kyi rang bzhin gcig tu shes pas /
NK016(ma)012:406: chos thams cad zhi khro rigs brgya'i 'khor lor dag cing /
NK016(ma)012:407: de yang gsang chen rigs gcig tu rnam par dag pa las /
NK016(ma)012:408: bzlas brjod ting nge 'dzin sogs ci byed thams cad
NK016(ma)012:409: kyang 'khor 'das rgya thag gi rol pa chen por
NK016(ma)012:410: spyad par bya ba yin no //
NK016(ma)012:411: de ltar slob bu'i blo'i rim pa dang sbyar te khrid la /
NK016(ma)012:412: g.yo thob goms brtan mthar phyin lnga'i nyams dang rtogs
NK016(ma)012:413: pa skyed rim nas ngo sprod pa dang gegs sel
NK016(ma)012:414: bogs 'don rnams nyams myong can gyis legs par gdams
NK016(ma)012:415: te khrid pas nyams rtogs yar ngo'i zla ba ltar
NK016(ma)012:416: 'phel te rim par tshogs sbyor gyi lam bgrod nas
NK016(ma)012:417: / slob pa'i zung 'jug rig 'dzin bzhi dang /
NK016(ma)012:418: mi slob pa'i zung 'jug dpal kun tu bzang po'i go 'phang la sbyor bar gdon mi za'o //
NK016(ma)012:419: ngag brjod bsam pa'i yul 'das dbang bzhi'i don //
NK016(ma)012:420: tshul bzhin nyams blangs lhag pa chos kyi sku //
NK016(ma)012:421: zung 'jug dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yi //
NK016(ma)012:422: go 'phang bla med thob phyir 'di bsngo'o //
NK016(ma)012:423: zhes na rag dong sprugs kyi dbang don ji ltar
NK016(ma)012:424: nyams su len pa'i khrid yig 'di yang blo ldan
NK016(ma)012:425: dge slong o rgyan bsod nams kyis bskul ba'i ngor
NK016(ma)012:426: / gter chen chos kyi rgyal po'i bka' drin gyis
NK016(ma)012:427: 'tsho ba'i gnyos kyi dge slong rmongs pa d+harma sh+r+ais
NK016(ma)012:428: sbyar ba'i yi ge pa ni legs gling chos mdzad
NK016(ma)012:429: dge slong 'gyur med mchog grub kyis bgyis pa dge
